                     ArcSoft Commander Version 1.0.0
                            Change Log

Version: 1.0.0
============================================================
Add Feature: 1+1/m+n master/slave backup.
Add Feature: task management.
Add Feature: remote storage management.
Add Feature: security management.
Add Feature: agent status monitor.
Add Feature: date time and time zone settings.
Add Feature: reboot / shutdown server.
Add Feature: DNS settings.
Add Feature: firewall settings.
Add Feature: route settings.
Add Feature: network settings.
Add Feature: remove group
Add Feature: rename group
Add Feature: remove server
Add Feature: rename server
Add Feature: add server(s) to exist group
Add Feature: creating 1+1/m+n group.
Add Feature: cluster base functions.
